title: Trump Greenland TariffThreat Risks NewUS-Europe Trade War
description: Donald Trump’s threat to hit European countries with a 10% levy over his claim on Greenland risks a new trade war between the US and the EU. Alex Morgan explains. (Source: Bloomberg)
